rows.label: tlk41400011_04_msg0001
rows.name: You have the air of an owner about you.

rows.label: tlk41400011_04_msg0002
rows.name:
What do you think happens when you
buy every single product in a shop?

rows.label: tlk41400011_04_msg0003
rows.name:
The shopkeeper, thinking you
must love their shop, will
urge you to become its owner.

rows.label: tlk41400011_04_msg0004
rows.name:
Becoming an owner requires a
considerable amount of money, but
there should be great benefits as well.
